WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.719
Shah Rukh Khan: Watching the
grinding stones, the Light, Kabir Cries

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:08.799
Inside the Two Stones, no one survives.

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.199
At the age of 24,

00:00:10.200 --> 00:00:13.439
Pralhad Tipanaya first
heard Kabir’s verses,

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:16.536
and at that moment this village
teacher’s being changed forever.

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:19.719
It’s over thirty years

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:23.279
since this school teacher has
taken Kabir’s soulful couplets

00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:24.679
and social ideas

00:00:24.680 --> 00:00:26.839
in the form of music

00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:29.600
to every corner
of the country and the world.